attributes.action: Increase funding to identify new treatments and cures for migraines
attributes.additional_details: For as long as I can remember I have suffered from debilitating migraines. We need to find a cure for this invisible disability. There are so many triggers for so many people. There must be something that can help.
attributes.background: The Government should recognise the debilitating impact migraines can have on sufferers and increase funding to identify new treatments and cures for migraines.
